/usr/local/bin/rttytx_writer.sh
/etc/systemd/system/rttytx.service

ezeket service fileokat tedd helyére, utána:


sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/rttytx_writer.sh

sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl enable rttytx.service
sudo systemctl start rttytx.service
sudo systemctl status rttytx.service


